                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18311201-247-victim1882 t18311201-247-viclabel1318"></join> - I was out with his bread on the 25th of November; I left my basket at the corner of <placeName id="t18311201-247-crimeloc1319">Portman-square</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18311201-247-crimeloc1319" type="placeName" value="Portman-square"></interp>
